Package: libcoin
Title: Linear Test Statistics for Permutation Inference
Date: 2016-09-01
Version: 0.6-0
Authors@R: person("Torsten", "Hothorn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "Torsten.Hothorn@R-project.org")
Description: Basis infrastructure for linear test statistics and permutation
  inference in the Strasser-Weber framework. This package must not be used
  by end-users. CRAN package coin implements all user interfaces and is
  ready to be used by anyone.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: stats, mvtnorm
Suggests: coin (>= 2.0-0)
LinkingTo: mvtnorm
License: GPL-2
